{"tid":2094911,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果日本人有類似大陸廣闊領土和資源，有冇機會挑戰美國地位？","createTime":"2020-07-05T05:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T05:54:32.000Z","uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9f3693acbaf9516cc677012870141ae19db8e9","tid":2094911,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成為東亞甚至全球霸主！"},{"pid":"88c943b29b090de1bf74dbd380c5149bacaa76e7","tid":2094911,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:17:12.000Z","msg":"唔發動二戰 依家繼續統治庫頁島 朝鮮台灣同東三省既話我覺得係有可能既"},{"pid":"af653458f855478dbabfcdd2c43b2b258efac78e","tid":2094911,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b9f3693acbaf9516cc677012870141ae19db8e9","tid":2094911,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成為東亞甚至全球霸主！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"8 90年代日本曾經經濟上挑戰美國地位所以先搞到經濟爆破<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李家超及香港警務處就是勾結外國勢力的最好例子<br />\n<br />\n美國參議員scott perry 公然要求特朗普承認香港及西藏是獨立國家擺明係顛覆國家政權分裂中國國土<br />\n<br />\n呢一樣嘢已經違反咗國安法第38條即使係鬼佬都可以喺外國拘捕佢，但係香港政府、香港警務處、李家超到依家今時今日並未對該位參議員發出通緝令及拘捕令<br />\n<br />\n我個人認為香港警隊及警務處應該係收咗美國佬錢分裂國家主權，點解唔落實國安法拘捕該名美國參議員？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E9%BB%A8%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1-%E7%9B%BC%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-214500608.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E7%259C%25BE%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%259